===Verb===
'''to elope''' (elopes, eloping, eloped, eloped)
#{{intransitive}} Of a married woman: To [[run away]] from home with a [[paramour]].
#{{intransitive}} Of a girl: To [[run away]] from home with a lover for the purpose of getting [[married]].
